        <updateDate>2007-11-28T18:11:23Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Fair Judicial Compensation Act of 2007 - Increases by 16.5% the annual salaries of the Chief Justice of the United States, associate justices of the Supreme Court, U.S. circuit judges, U.S. district judges, and judges of the United States Court of International Trade.</p><p>Amends the federal bankruptcy code to increase fees for bankruptcy trustees.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
